---
layout: base.njk
title: Tamburello360 - La Casa Indipendente del Tamburello Italiano
---

{% set hasEnrichedMatches = collections.partiteEnriched and collections.partiteEnriched.length > 0 %}
{% set hasSerieAStandings = collections.classificheSerieA and collections.classificheSerieA.length > 0 and collections.classificheSerieA[0].data.teams %}

{# 1. HERO STAGE: CINEMATOGRAFICA #}
<section class="hero-stage">
  <div class="hero-bg-container">
    <div class="hero-vignette"></div>
    <img src="/images/uploads/hero-bg.jpg" alt="Tamburello Action" class="hero-img">
  </div>

  <div class="container hero-main-content">
    <div class="hero-branding">
      <span class="hero-badge">Progetto Indipendente</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">POLVERE.<br><span class="highlight">GLORIA.</span><br>TAMBURELLO.</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">L'anima del tamburello italiano raccontata da chi lo vive ogni giorno.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-group">
        <a href="/partite/" class="btn btn-primary">Match Center</a>
        <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn-outline">Storie di Campo</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-sidebar-data">
      {% if hasEnrichedMatches %}
        {% set nextMatch = collections.partiteEnriched | selectattr("is_recommended", "equalto", true) | first %}
        {% if nextMatch %}
        <div class="hero-featured-match">
          <span class="live-indicator">Match Center</span>
          <div class="match-teams-box">
            <span>{{ nextMatch.home_team.name }}</span>
            <small>VS</small>
            <span>{{ nextMatch.away_team.name }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="match-footer">
            {{ nextMatch.date_day_label }} ore {{ nextMatch.date_time_label }}
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endif %}

      <div class="hero-standings-mini">
        <small>Top 3 Serie A</small>
        {% if hasSerieAStandings %}
          {% for team in collections.classificheSerieA[0].data.teams | limit(3) %}
            <div class="standing-row">
              <span>{{ team.name }}</span>
              <strong>{{ team.points }}</strong>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-live-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ticker-wrap">
        <div class="ticker-scroll">
          {% for match in collections.partiteRecenti | limit(6) %}
            <span class="ticker-match">
              <strong>{{ match.home_team.name }}</strong>
              {{ match.score_label }}
              <strong>{{ match.away_team.name }}</strong>
            </span>
          {% endfor %}
          {% for match in collections.partiteRecenti | limit(6) %}
            <span class="ticker-match">
              <strong>{{ match.home_team.name }}</strong>
              {{ match.score_label }}
              <strong>{{ match.away_team.name }}</strong>
            </span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# 3. MAGAZINE SECTION: LOOK EDITORIALE #}
<section class="container section-padding">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Storie di <span class="highlight">Campo</span></h2>
    <a href="/blog/">Tutti gli articoli &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="magazine-layout">
    {% set posts = collections.blogVisible %}
    {% if posts.length > 0 %}
      <article class="post-featured">
        <div class="post-img-wrapper">
          <img src="{{ posts[0].data.image }}" alt="{{ posts[0].data.title }}">
        </div>
        <div class="post-content">
          <span class="post-category">{{ posts[0].data.category }}</span>
          <h3><a href="{{ posts[0].url }}">{{ posts[0].data.title }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ posts[0].data.excerpt | truncate(150) }}</p>
          <time>{{ posts[0].data.date | readableDate }}</time>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="post-sidebar">
        {% for post in posts | slice(1, 3) %}
          <article class="post-mini">
            <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
            <div>
              <h4><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h4>
              <time>{{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

{# 4. DATA & MISSION: CONTRASTO VISIVO #}
<section class="split-section">
  <div class="container split-grid">
    <div class="standings-snapshot">
      {% if hasSerieAStandings %}
        {% set classificaA = collections.classificheSerieA[0] %}
        <h3>Classifica Serie A <span class="year">{{ classificaA.data.year or '' }}</span></h3>
        <table class="mini-table">
          {% for team in classificaA.data.teams | limit(5) %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ team.position }}&deg;</td>
            <td class="team-name">{{ team.name }}</td>
            <td class="points">{{ team.points }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </table>
        <a href="/classifiche/" class="btn-text">Vedi classifica completa</a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div id="progetto" class="mission-box">
      <div class="mission-tag">Chi Siamo</div>
      <h3>Non &egrave; solo un sito. &Egrave; un <span class="highlight">omaggio</span>.</h3>
      <p>Tamburello360 nasce dal desiderio di non lasciar scomparire la narrazione di uno sport che &egrave; storia, polvere e talento. Gestiamo i dati in modo automatico per lasciar spazio a ci&ograve; che conta: il racconto delle persone e dei territori.</p>
      <div class="signature">Creato con &#10084; da un appassionato</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# 5. COMMUNITY CTA #}
<section class="community-cta">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Entra nel <span class="highlight">Cerchio</span></h2>
    <p>Segui i nostri aggiornamenti live e le storie dai campi su Instagram.</p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#" class="social-btn ig">Instagram</a>
      <a href="#" class="social-btn telegram">Telegram Risultati</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
